text:
Why do i get these warnings 
[WARNING] Unknown Ptg 3c (60).

i think 3C is record id for Continue record and poi has this record implemented 
from day one.

Any clues??

ashish.

There are not record id, these are ptg Id's which are quite different, relevant
only for formulas. 3C is PtgRefErr3D, which is essentially a #REF in your sheet.
Remove that, and the warning will go away.
